{"tid":2003220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實連和你Sing都未聚到人，咁快搞遊行好似有危險～","createTime":"2020-05-05T15:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T16:10:19.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"42a3ff5e9f3f5347254a16b14efc93a9eea7d2e2","tid":2003220,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T15:49:52.000Z","msg":"我知大家好期侍510 大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但大家問心有眼睇，根本連和你Sing 人數係完全唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而連登D行動Post 係永遠推唔起，成個抗爭氣氛同舊年差一段距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （可能大家關注選舉比重多左）<br />\n<br />\n如個貿貿然間硬搞遊行，根據經驗，人數一唔夠就好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要510 好大機會因為限聚令下拎唔到不反，咁樣人數只會更少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以係大家未有大共識下，510好可能係運動以來最危險既一次遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c554f366ad803107ee72a6ff3cf4391ce032b7","tid":2003220,"uid":52839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"好多和理非淨係去遊行"},{"pid":"e46a936ccd94b1f699b86b683fbf317d3b7d3d57","tid":2003220,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T15:52:41.000Z","msg":"一係全世界都話去<br />\n<br />\n一係全世界都話不了<br />\n<br />\n照連登現在氣氛係各佔一半<br />\n<br />\n咁樣係最最最危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c67784230b13b1ada8d61d9db5fff26eaefb2cb","tid":2003220,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T15:56:13.000Z","msg":"又開post分化<br />\n善用起底"},{"pid":"3691b4eeed9e603d3a03bf9b664b7992